reactor-tcp 1.0.0.BUILD-SNAPSHOT API

Packages 
Package Description
reactor.tcp
Components for writing TCP-based clients and servers using Reactor abstractions.
reactor.tcp.config
Configuration of the various TCP parameters for clients and servers.
reactor.tcp.encoding
Components to handling encoding and decoding of objects into network-capable byte streams and .Buffer Buffers.
reactor.tcp.encoding.json
Encoding and decoding using the JSON format.
reactor.tcp.encoding.syslog
Decoding using the syslog format.
reactor.tcp.netty
Implementations of the various TCP abstractions based on Netty.
reactor.tcp.spec
Specs provide a fluent DSL for building TcpClients and TcpServers using common configuration options.
reactor.tcp.ssl
Support classes for Reactor's TCP SSL support.
